OL,6,FA mum and her partner from Cornwall
OL,7,Fhave been jailed for planning to rape
OL,8,Fher six-year-old daughter.
OL,10,FThe pair, who cannot be named in order
OL,11,Fto protect the identity of the victim,
OL,12,Fwere sentenced at Plymouth Crown Court
OL,13,Fon Friday 30 August.
OL,15,FThe woman, from East Cornwall, was
OL,16,Fjailed for 17 years and the man, from
OL,17,FNorth Cornwall, for 13 years. They
OL,18,Fwere both given Sexual Harm Prevention
OL,19,FOrder for 20 years.
