OL,6,FPolice began an investigation in 2021
OL,7,Fafter the man left his phone with
OL,8,Fsomeone in a pub, where they saw
OL,9,Fconcerning messages relating to the
OL,10,Fsexual abuse of a young girl.
OL,12,FOfficers seized the phone as evidence
OL,13,Fand arrested the man and woman.
OL,15,FDuring the investigation, detectives
OL,16,Ffound text messages which showed that
OL,17,Fthey were planning for the woman to
OL,18,Fdrug her child, aged six, in order for
OL,19,Fthe man to rape her.
