OL,7,Fimages of the child that the woman had
OL,8,Ftaken and sent to him.
OL,10,FThe woman was charged with five
OL,11,Foffences, which she pleaded not guilty
OL,12,Fto.
OL,14,FAt a trial held at Truro Crown Court
OL,15,Fin May 2024, she was found unanimously
OL,16,Fguilty by a jury and was jailed for 17
OL,17,Fyears for the following offences:
