OL,6,FThe man pleaded guilty to charges of
OL,7,Fconspiracy to rape a child under 13
OL,8,Fand possessing indecent images of a
OL,9,Fchild. He was jailed for 13 years.
OL,11,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Sara Ward said:
OL,13,F"This is an extremely harrowing case,
OL,14,Fand we welcome the sentences handed
OL,15,Fdown by the judge today.
OL,17,F"I would like to thank everyone who
OL,18,Fhas supported the police investigation
OL,19,Fthrough what has been a very long and
OL,20,Fchallenging investigation due to the
OL,21,Fnature of the crimes.
